				// Typography
				article#css-type
					.page-header
						h3 Typography

					section#css-type-paragraphs
						h4 Paragraphs
						p.
							FrontKit's <code>#{"<body>"}</code> and all paragraphs get, by default, a <code>font-size</code> of <b>14px</b> and a <code>line-height</code> of <b>20px</b>,
							which looks very good to read. Also, paragraphs get an extra bottom margin, to better separate things.

						.docs-example
							p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas gravida, mi vitae ultricies bibendum, justo metus ultricies tortor, eget aliquet quam risus et turpis. Integer sed ornare nibh. Vivamus eget purus velit, sed vehicula ligula.
							p Nullam eget erat arcu. Phasellus sit amet augue eget mauris pulvinar posuere. Pellentesque convallis semper libero vitae ultrices. Donec egestas vehicula mauris ac porttitor. Donec quis urna ac tellus facilisis sollicitudin non eget purus.
							p Proin tortor nunc, scelerisque pulvinar ultricies sodales, imperdiet eget sem. Donec nec neque et ligula tristique porta in nec risus. Cras id faucibus diam. Phasellus lacus mauris, vulputate ac aliquam at, mattis et velit. Cras eu ante nisi, ac ornare neque. Morbi auctor mollis orci. Nam aliquam luctus semper. Cras varius lacinia vulputate.

						h5 Lead paragraph
						p If you need to make some paragraph stand out from the rest, just add to it the <code>lead</code> class:</p>
						.docs-example
							p.lead Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas gravida, mi vitae ultricies bibendum, justo metus ultricies tortor, eget aliquet quam risus et turpis.

					section#css-type-headings
